Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)\a6}製作 ？ 秋月暮葉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.03,0:01:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a3}Pennisuia Colheita     五月13日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.36,0:01:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lenine! Lenine!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我馬上就做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能相信嗎？ 現在你的指尖觸摸到了我的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,標題：無聊涂鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.28,0:03:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你 我會出好價錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么樣？ 好價錢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！ 喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Juan 「雨中的Tucano(犀鳥)」那本書到哪里去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.49,0:03:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰買的？ 女孩子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 像小女孩一樣的老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那輛破摩托車
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫"還要花點時間"啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明Hiroshi就在眼前了 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.37,0:04:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了Hatchin 有話就說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要書
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.63,0:04:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書？ 什么書？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年帶著從籠中放出的鳥兒一起去旅行的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.18,0:04:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去尋找那只鳥兒的父母
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Laranja的時候 我時不時地會看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.14,0:04:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是因為Michiko來了 最后的結局沒能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 你去買吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以現在就去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過Hatchin 只能給你10Arca
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:04:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超過這個數 絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.76,0:05:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a3}五月14日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.85,0:05:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鮮度最高 早市限定優惠的蔬菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.50,0:05:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每種東西都只要1Arca多一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些番茄怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是Plano Colheita特產的怪物番茄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.43,0:05:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名為Monstro
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1個相當于25個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里只有我家有賣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送貨來的是這些家伙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.44,0:05:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！ 你的腳！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別左顧右盼的 看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:05:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么樣 這個扛著番茄的帥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.91,0:06:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魚 剛捕獲的鮮魚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,價格優惠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魚 魚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.46,0:06:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買了不少東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是人家讓我幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 那本書賣掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「雨中的Tocano」 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的 不...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.12,0:06:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin 你在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你原來叫Hatchin啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.91,0:07:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天中午我會等你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天3點 鐘響的時候 在教堂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.98,0:08:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問多少錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要錢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.24,0:08:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.97,0:08:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你能陪我一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.23,0:08:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin是第一次來這里？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.75,0:09:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 Hatchin你為什么來Peninsula
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 請不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個稱呼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫Lenine 大概是叫這個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為大家都這么叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫Hana... 我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了尋找父親 一直在旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去Plano
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是摩托車壞了 暫時停留在這里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了尋找父親 一直旅行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和「雨中的Tocano」一樣 !
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我還是無法收下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.86,0:10:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"抓到你了 微風"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書上是這么寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.36,0:10:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種叫Tocano的鳥 是這個國家沒有的鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.12,0:10:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶著她開始旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.69,0:10:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的地是她所希望的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.61,0:11:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是在樓下等你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.21,0:11:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是給Michiko的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.28,0:11:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.92,0:11:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.13,0:12:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并沒有恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.04,0:12:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我依然還愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.22,0:12:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你回來啦 明天出發
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.05,0:13:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩托車修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.16,0:13:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko 這本書
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個看起來像人妖的家伙丟下的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.69,0:13:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來明天就出發了 你準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.53,0:13:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別垂頭喪氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得不分手 這點最初你就明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,0:13:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看了？ 你看過這個了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.56,0:13:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 你看了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.93,0:13:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是Lenine？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.03,0:13:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才干了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫 是不是第一次被男人追 高興的要飛起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.88,0:13:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事情都扯上男人 不要把我當成你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 你丫要不是Hiroshi的女兒的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.71,0:14:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才你就死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我是成年人 可以原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這本書 請交給那個叫Lenine的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.77,0:14:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你嗎 他所說的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.48,0:14:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關系 我會轉交給他的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.84,0:15:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我還是自己還給他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他沒有說事故的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.54,0:15:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他沒有記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了事故 在三丁目的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.77,0:15:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煤氣泄漏導致爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.88,0:15:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被炸飛的什么東西好像撞擊到了Lenine的頭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等他睜開眼睛的時候一切都被忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外Lenine和以前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.10,0:15:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也好過去也很好像鳥兒一樣自由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記憶一定會恢復的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這下子在失憶期間的記憶會丟失 大部分情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時你能微笑著面對他嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:16:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有今天了 明天我就要出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去Plano
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.95,0:16:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來不是來見你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 能遇見你Hana我要向所有的一切表示感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得找到了什么非常重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:17:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是會忘記吧 忘記一切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.74,0:17:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 你遭遇事故的事情 沒有記憶的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會忘的 絕對不會忘的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道自己是怎樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.62,0:17:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連這個自己生長的城市看上去就像個陌生世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.27,0:17:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身處于空白的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.20,0:17:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下清晰的腳印 向前前進
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.29,0:17:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還是空白的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.43,0:17:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一滴一滴的記憶會為這個世界帶來色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關于你的記憶也深深刻在我的心里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.88,0:17:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.03,0:17:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再讓我心煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.37,0:17:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 討厭死你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.59,0:18:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我還不想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}五月15日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 沒見過你呢 是來旅游的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.88,0:19:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎「雨中的Tucano」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.01,0:19:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.63,0:19:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是讀了之后心情就會變得幸福的魔法般的書
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不騙你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經想讓住在這里的女孩看這本書
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少和你有些相似的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.34,0:19:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到她的時候 我想這個世界上是有天使的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.90,0:19:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為懼怕這個現實 我一直在沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.60,0:19:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午就出發了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你收拾好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不會幫你收拾的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.54,0:20:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.66,0:20:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 那時真的非常高興...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:20:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好難受 好難受...
